akouts before you even see them</p></span></div><div data-rid="fc63293d-2d28-4fab-9835-b7b254ad7922" class="r-1iurtuo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Teenage hormonal acne doesn’t appear overnight, it forms under the skin days before.</p><p>By using the Clear Skin Kit consistently, teens report fewer surprise breakouts because it helps interrupt pimples before they fully form.</p><p>This means clearer skin between cycles, not just during flare-ups.</p><p><br></p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="23be68b0-0a2e-4ec7-a886-cef5db77444b" class="r-o6p9sp"><picture data-rid="a092d940-64e5-4376-873a-1b319ed10e57" class="r-10ya5vt"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/126d60c0-cd59-49e0-bb59-8b65c933ead2?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/126d60c0-cd59-49e0-bb59-8b65c933ead2?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/126d60c0-cd59-49e0-bb59-8b65c933ead2?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/126d60c0-cd59-49e0-bb59-8b65c933ead2" alt="Skincare product textures arranged on a blue background with steps and descriptions labeled." class="r-sz0ypk" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="082db6ce-c4e3-40e6-a94f-029905b8997a" class="r-8q91qp"><div data-rid="df017ca2-4f8a-47cd-abce-719fd87bf867" class="r-mfltyc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>5. Gentle enough to use every single day, on young skin(year-round)</p></span></div><div data-rid="1d1cdbf6-49e5-447f-8c68-442425cae94d" class="r-oatq9v alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Unlike harsh acne treatments that dry you out or cause irritation, this routine is:</p><ul><li><p>Gentle</p></li><li><p>Hydrating</p></li><li><p>Safe for sensitive skin and teen skin</p></li></ul><p>You don’t need to “stop and start” depending on your skin, it’s designed for daily use, even when your skin is calm.</p><p><br></p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="91111fc0-1ec5-42a6-a073-305368e64cd2" class="r-1b03w8s"><picture data-rid="be6b14d3-1593-4df9-89f3-7d5302f2d474" class="r-16zmypa"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/f2b0fb65-0e1e-44fd-87da-6cd87289f916?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/f2b0fb65-0e1e-44fd-87da-6cd87289f916?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/f2b0fb65-0e1e-44fd-87da-6cd87289f916?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/f2b0fb65-0e1e-44fd-87da-6cd87289f916" class="r-fyev22" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="af17117c-d59e-49f7-8524-0a75853717c2" class="r-c2b9t5"><div data-rid="dbfbf829-7109-421f-8e3b-5423d8454bb4" class="r-1u43q5x alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>6. Safe to use for teens</p></span></div><div data-rid="bd455639-ae31-465a-99b4-1df500b62f78" class="r-1qlcxr2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Many acne products aren’t teenager safe, which makes hormonal acne even harder to treat.</p><p>The Clear Skin Kit is:</p><ul><li><p>Teenager Sage</p></li><li><p>Free from harsh actives</p></li><li><p>Designed to support skin through hormonal changes</p></li></ul><p>That includes acne due to puberty. </p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="e983de94-6a43-4463-8958-9ade7d982377" class="r-1t3mcv9"><picture data-rid="1afdc92c-7ceb-4523-8d8c-b872cc304afe" class="r-1aazori"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/26ca684e-2934-498b-acbd-dc9b0e18d8bd?width=820" med